<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١١٧٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1038">تَوْبَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6390">مُوَرِّقٍ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«قُلْتُ لِابْنِ عُمَرَ <span class="special">﵄</span>: أَتُصَلِّي الضُّحَى؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> لَا،<span class="c5"> قُلْتُ:</span> فَعُمَرُ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> لَا،<span class="c5"> قُلْتُ:</span> فَأَبُو بَكْرٍ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> لَا،<span class="c5"> قُلْتُ:</span> فَالنَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> لَا إِخَالُهُ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>